import React from 'react'

import {Section,
        Header,
        Title,
        Description,
        RepoContainer,
        Icons,
        StarNumber

} from './styles'

import { BiStar} from "react-icons/bi"

const Repos_Page = (props) => {


    return (
        <Section>
            <Header>{props.number} repositórios</Header>
            <RepoContainer>
                {(props?.repo)}
                <Title>Repositórios de </Title>
                <Description>Projeto que foi feito para poder acessar em tempo real o valor de criptommoedas</Description>
                <Icons>
                <BiStar size={15} /> <StarNumber>35</StarNumber>
                </Icons>
             
            </RepoContainer>
            
            
        </Section>
    )
}

export default Repos_Page
